text: SENER is a private engineering and technology group founded in 1956. Specialises in activities related to Engineering and Construction. The company has industrial holdings in companies and works in the areas of energy, environment and aeronautics. In 2021, the Perseverance rover lands on Mars with SENER Aerospace technology on board. == References == Category:Technology companies of Spain Category:1956 establishments in Europe Category:Technology companies of Europe
